headline: Philip Morris International to Host Webcast of 2025 First-Quarter Results
summary: STAMFORD, CT, April 16, 2025--Regulatory News: Philip Morris International Inc. (PMI) (NYSE: PM) will host a live audio webcast at www.pmi.com/2025Q1earnings on Wednesday, April 23, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. ET, to discuss its 2025 first-quarter financial results, which will be issued at approximately 7:00 a.m. ET the same day.
